item.title: How do i log on a 508 server
item.dc:creator: @abctest123abc abctest123abc
item.description:
@abctest123abc wrote:

If ur running the server u have to type in 127.0.0.1 in server ip name
If u not running the server u have to download a other 508 client because ipchanger doesnt work at all 508 servers
